{"id":232394497,"title":"有喜歡民族金屬或民族搖滾的同好嗎?","content":"https://youtu.be/jM8dCGIm6yc\n\nhttps://youtu.be/v4xZUr0BEfE\n\n最近一直聽這團，The Hu ，來自蒙古的搖滾團，雖然蒙古金屬團一直都不少，但憑兩首歌就橫空蓋世的團體真的不多。\n\n由於自己一直都有在研究蒙古與圖瓦的泛音唱腔「呼麥」(Humei)，所以當他們運用此唱腔唱死金和搖滾曲目，每每都讓我為之一振。似乎只有用金屬和搖滾樂，才能表現出蒙古民族血液裡的不屈精神。\n(當然金屬樂出現的本身，就和大量以工業發展的地區有很強烈的關聯，這裡先不贅述)\n\n題外話，前一陣子才剛有「兩岸文化交流協會」來臺灣主辦的「蒙古非物質文化遺產」演出，讓我覺得值得討論的是，這些器樂與舞蹈形成一種屬於「中國國族精神」的特徵取向時，到底他們所表現出來的是誰的蒙古，誰的身份認同呢？\nhttps://youtu.be/Ji8G-McTAp8","excerpt":"最近一直聽這團，The Hu ，來自蒙古的搖滾團，雖然蒙古金屬團一直都不少，但憑兩首歌就橫空蓋世的團體真的不多。由於自己一直都有在研究蒙古與圖瓦的泛音唱腔「呼麥」（Humei），所以當他們運用此唱腔唱","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"97eb486d-2f9d-4912-8b5d-b8f539e449d4","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-29T03:41:02.978Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-29T03:45:50.614Z","commentCount":5,"likeCount":19,"tags":[],"topics":["獨立樂團","非主流音樂","樂團","音樂","蒙古"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"獨立音樂","forumAlias":"indiemusic","school":"國立臺南藝術大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":19}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"40eb1e1b-44a5-4069-beb3-4908f6800593","url":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/jM8dCGIm6yc/hqdefault.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/jM8dCGIm6yc/hqdefault.jpg","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/jM8dCGIm6yc/hqdefault.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-29T03:41:02.978Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-29T03:45:50.614Z"},{"id":"40eb1e1b-44a5-4069-beb3-4908f6800593","url":"https://youtu.be/jM8dCGIm6yc","normalizedUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jM8dCGIm6yc","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/jM8dCGIm6yc/hqdefault.jpg","type":"video/youtube","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-29T03:41:02.978Z","upd